  <VAE_StrengthenedByBond.label>牵绊加成</VAE_StrengthenedByBond.label>
  <!-- EN: This animal is bonded to one of the colonists and it will be considerably strengtened. However, if the bonded colonist dies, the animal will leave the map and be forever lost. -->
